Display your freshly picked flowers in a classic ceramic Studded vase.Or let it be the artificial one’s.This vibrant vase can also be used as a utensil holder.The perfect gift for that special person in your life from the house of Tied Ribbons. Handcrafted by indian artisans and shipped across the seas to captivate your hearts.

More of the artificial flowers and vases range also available.Soap Case, Toothbrush Holder and Soap Dispenser with white Color crafted with Porcelain Dispenser Capacity is 250 ml.
